    <briefdescription>
<para>Debounced 2-position GPIO switch — sends a ControlPacket CAN event on change. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Mirrors DcsBios::Switch2Pos but sends a CAN packet via <ref refid="namespacePanelGroup_1a21b5d03ffa53faaa9e4a7bd9759b0443" kindref="member">PanelGroup::sendEvent()</ref> instead of writing to DCS-BIOS directly. The matching OpenSkyhawk::DCSInput on the <ref refid="namespaceSimGateway" kindref="compound">SimGateway</ref> translates the packet to a DCS-BIOS message.</para>
<para>Value sent: 1 when pin is LOW (switch closed to GND), 0 when HIGH.</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classOpenSkyhawk_1_1Switch2Pos" kindref="compound">OpenSkyhawk::Switch2Pos</ref><sp/>ejSafe(A_4E_C_SEAT_EJECT_SAFE,<sp/>PA1);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
